text.calc: *   You can only register for sessions on the day they occur and from 21:00 the night before.*   You cannot register for multiple sessions in the same time slot.*   You can de-register from a session to change your mind.*   You can de-register and register for sessions up to 30 minutes after the session starts.*   You can provide feedback for sessions from 30 minutes after the session starts until      the end of the day.*   Any per session delegate limit will be enforced on the system.*   The timeout for inactivity is only 2 minutes.
